---
title: "Sequence Diagram: Members Invitation Service"
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor Owner     as Owner (Inviter)
    actor Recipient as Recipient
    participant FE  as Frontend<br/>(React/Ionic)
    participant MS  as MembersService<br/>(port 8001)
    participant JWT as JWTHandler<br/>(Infra/Security)
    participant ES  as Email Sender<br/>(SMTP/SendGrid)
    participant DB  as PostgreSQL

    Note over Owner,DB: ── SEND INVITATION ─────────────────────────────────────

    Owner ->> FE  : Fill invitation form<br/>{ recipient_email, permission (READER|EDITOR),<br/>camera_ids, expires_at }
    activate FE
    FE    ->> MS  : POST /api/v1/members/invitations<br/>Authorization: Bearer <token>
    activate MS
    MS    ->> JWT : verify_token(token, "access")
    activate JWT
    JWT  -->> MS  : { user_id, email }
    deactivate JWT

    MS    ->> DB  : SELECT pending invitations<br/>WHERE inviter_user_id=? AND recipient_email=?
    activate DB
    DB   -->> MS  : [ existing ] | []
    deactivate DB

    alt Duplicate pending invitation exists
        MS   -->> FE  : 409 Conflict { detail: "Invitation already pending" }
        FE   -->> Owner : Show error toast
    else No conflict → create invitation
        MS    ->> MS  : OTPGenerator.generate_alphanumeric(8) → "A3F9K2BX"<br/>bcrypt.hash(raw_code) → code_hash
        MS    ->> DB  : INSERT INTO invitations<br/>( inviter_user_id, inviter_email, recipient_email,<br/>permission, status='pending', code_hash,<br/>code_expires_at=NOW()+48h, unlimited, expires_at )<br/>INSERT INTO invitation_cameras ( invitation_id, camera_id ) × N
        activate DB
        DB   -->> MS  : { invitation_id, created_at }
        deactivate DB
        MS    ->> ES  : send_invitation_email<br/>( recipient_email, raw_code,<br/>permission, camera_names, expires_at )
        activate ES
        ES   -->> MS  : Delivered
        deactivate ES
        MS   -->> FE  : 201 Created { invitation_id, status: "pending" }
        FE   -->> Owner : "Invitation sent to [email]"
    end
    deactivate MS

    Note over Owner,DB: ── VIEW RECEIVED INVITATIONS ────────────────────────────

    Recipient ->> FE  : Open "My Invitations" panel
    FE        ->> MS  : GET /api/v1/members/invitations/received<br/>Authorization: Bearer <token>
    activate MS
    MS        ->> DB  : SELECT * FROM invitations<br/>WHERE recipient_email=? AND status='pending'
    activate DB
    DB       -->> MS  : [ Invitation records ]
    deactivate DB
    MS       -->> FE  : 200 [{ id, inviter_email, permission, camera_ids, expires_at }]
    deactivate MS
    FE       -->> Recipient : Show pending invitations with Accept / Decline

    Note over Owner,DB: ── RESPOND TO INVITATION ────────────────────────────────

    alt Recipient accepts
        Recipient ->> FE  : Click "Accept" + enter code "A3F9K2BX"
        FE        ->> MS  : POST /api/v1/members/invitations/{id}/accept<br/>{ code: "A3F9K2BX" }
        activate MS
        MS        ->> DB  : SELECT * FROM invitations WHERE id = ?
        activate DB
        DB       -->> MS  : Invitation record
        deactivate DB
        MS        ->> MS  : bcrypt.verify(code, code_hash) → True/False<br/>invitation.is_expired() → check expires_at

        alt Code invalid OR invitation expired
            MS   -->> FE  : 400 { detail: "Invalid or expired code" }
            FE   -->> Recipient : Show error
        else Valid code
            MS    ->> DB  : UPDATE invitations SET status='accepted', handled_at=NOW()<br/>INSERT INTO memberships ( owner_user_id, member_user_id,<br/>member_email, permission )<br/>INSERT INTO membership_cameras × N
            activate DB
            DB   -->> MS  : { membership_id }
            deactivate DB
            MS    ->> ES  : send_invitation_accepted_email(inviter_email)
            activate ES
            ES   -->> MS  : Delivered
            deactivate ES
            MS   -->> FE  : 201 { membership_id, permission, camera_ids }
            FE   -->> Recipient : "Access granted to N camera(s)"
        end
        deactivate MS

    else Recipient declines
        Recipient ->> FE  : Click "Decline"
        FE        ->> MS  : POST /api/v1/members/invitations/{id}/decline
        activate MS
        MS        ->> DB  : UPDATE invitations<br/>SET status='declined', handled_at=NOW()
        activate DB
        DB       -->> MS  : OK
        deactivate DB
        MS        ->> ES  : send_invitation_declined_email(inviter_email)
        activate ES
        ES       -->> MS  : Delivered
        deactivate ES
        MS       -->> FE  : 204 No Content
        FE       -->> Recipient : "Invitation declined"
        deactivate MS
    end

    deactivate FE
